.\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically, the IOC does not have digital rights in Europe and the UK, among others.\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, moving images from official Olympic venues and areas are geo-blocked for these markets, which is why the videos cannot be viewed.\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have not been deleted,\\\" the IOC stated.\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Decamps said Sunday during an IOC news conference that there was \\\"never an intention to disrespect any religious group,\\\"accordingto Deadline.\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4837, \"end\": 4845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 4942, \"to\": 5016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TRENDING  \\u00a92026 The Daily Caller, Inc.\", \"from\": 5018, \"to\": 5056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5044, \"end\": 5056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Daily_Caller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daily Calle